snippet.title: Frogar.io Promo Trailer
snippet.description:
Frogar.io is a frogtastic online game where you must eat your way to victory. Play against players from all over the world to become the biggest and baddest frog ever! Have you got what it takes? 

Frogar.io is available on...
- play in your browser: http://frogar.io
- android via google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...
- ios via the play store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/frogar-io/id1244037773

Find us on...
- facebook: https://www.facebook.com/frogario/
- twitter: https://twitter.com/Frogariogame
- instagram: https://www.instagram.com/frogario/
